issue_body:
```java
@InjectUser(config = CustomUser.class)
ManagedUser myAdmin;

public static class CustomUser implements UserConfig {
        @Override
        public UserConfigBuilder configure(UserConfigBuilder user) {
            return user.clientRoles(Constants.REALM_MANAGEMENT_CLIENT_ID, AdminRoles.REALM_ADMIN);
        }
}
```

`UserSupplier` doesn't assign these roles to the user. This issue was already tackled in https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak/pull/36828:
https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak/pull/36828/commits/55f5a2d326711fb757d3d36470f378f4892cc80c
